<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8061092>
    dc:description "FIGURES 121–134. Diatom taxa of Seogwipo coast in Jeju Island (13). Figs 121, 122. Amphora bigibba var. interrupta. Figs 123, 124. A. staurohyalina. Figs 125, 130. Nitzschia marginulata var. didyma. Figs 126, 127. Seminavis cf. pusilla. Figs 128, 129. Nitzschia composita. Figs 131, 132. Seminavis latior. Fig. 133. Tetramphora intermedia. Fig. 134. T. decussata. Scale bars = 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8061092/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

